%% Data Flow Diagram - Model Metadata Collection
%% Generated by: Claude Opus 4.6

sequenceDiagram
    participant Extractor as model-extractor<br/>Go CLI (Build-Time)
    participant HF_Collections as HuggingFace API<br/>Collections Endpoint<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant HF_Models as HuggingFace API<br/>Models Endpoint<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant HF_Readme as HuggingFace<br/>README Raw<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Registry as registry.redhat.io<br/>OCI Distribution v2<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant FS as Local Filesystem<br/>File I/O
    participant Konflux as Konflux CI/CD<br/>Tekton PipelineRun
    participant Quay as quay.io<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Consumer as RHOAI Platform<br/>(Model Catalog UI)

    Note over Extractor,Registry: Flow 1: Model Metadata Extraction and Catalog Generation

    Extractor->>HF_Collections: GET /api/users/RedHatAI/collections<br/>TLS 1.2+ | No Auth (public)
    HF_Collections-->>Extractor: Collection list (JSON)

    Extractor->>HF_Collections: GET /api/collections/{slug}<br/>TLS 1.2+ | No Auth
    HF_Collections-->>Extractor: Collection details with model refs

    Extractor->>Registry: GET OCI manifest + layers<br/>TLS 1.2+ | Docker auth
    Registry-->>Extractor: ModelCar manifests, model card layers

    Extractor->>HF_Models: GET /api/models/{name}<br/>TLS 1.2+ | No Auth
    HF_Models-->>Extractor: Model details (tags, license, etc.)

    Extractor->>HF_Readme: GET /{model}/raw/main/README.md<br/>TLS 1.2+ | No Auth
    HF_Readme-->>Extractor: README with YAML frontmatter

    Note over Extractor: Priority: (1) modelcard.md from OCI<br/>(2) HuggingFace YAML/API<br/>(3) Registry metadata<br/>(4) Generated defaults

    Extractor->>FS: Write output/ (individual model YAML)
    Extractor->>FS: Write data/models-catalog.yaml
    Extractor->>FS: Write data/validated-models-catalog.yaml

    Note over Konflux,Consumer: Flow 2: Container Image Build and Consumption

    Konflux->>Konflux: Clone GitHub repo<br/>443/TCP HTTPS | Git token
    Konflux->>Konflux: Build Dockerfile.konflux<br/>Static data copy to ubi9-micro
    Konflux->>Quay: Push multi-arch image<br/>(amd64, arm64, ppc64le, s390x)<br/>TLS 1.2+ | Service account
    Consumer->>Quay: Pull data container image<br/>TLS 1.2+ | Image pull secret
    Note over Consumer: Init container mounts /app/data/<br/>Reads models-catalog.yaml<br/>and validated-models-catalog.yaml
